item.title: Jail Glitch [PI]
item.dc:creator: @akshayp1 akshayp1
item.description:
@akshayp1 wrote:

I made a shops command that teleports you to the shops on my PI server and you can use this command to get out of jail. This is my shops command:

if (playerCommand.startsWith(“shops”)) {
if (!c.inWild()) {
c.getPA().movePlayer(2604, 3093, 0);
}
